OL,3,CWoman, 84, 'terrified' as tax office
OL,4,Csends her #1,600 bill
OL,6,FA 84-year-old pensioner from Guernsey
OL,7,Fhas racked up fines of around #1,600
OL,8,Fdespite insisting she always sorts her
OL,9,Ftax on time.
OL,11,FBrenda Wall from St Peter Port
OL,12,Freceived an email from the Revenue
OL,13,FService in March accusing her of not
OL,14,Fpaying the correct level of income
OL,15,Ftax, she has since been charged around
OL,16,F#10 per day.
OL,18,FShe says: "I'm terrified really, I've
OL,19,Fbeen on the phone to Mark to ask him,
OL,20,F'please help me'."
