OL,3,CWoman, 84, 'terrified' as tax office
OL,4,Csends her #1,600 bill
OL,6,FBrenda and her son Mark say they have
OL,7,Fconsistently tried to get in contact
OL,8,Fwith the Tax Office to straighten out
OL,9,Fthe issue but never received a reply.
OL,11,FMark Wall explains: "My mother is
OL,12,Fbeing fined frightening sums of money.
OL,13,FShe's always paid her tax on time, so
OL,14,Fwe really don't understand why all of
OL,15,Fa sudden she's being accused of not
OL,16,Fdoing so.
