OL,3,CWoman, 84, 'terrified' as tax office
OL,4,Csends her #1,600 bill
OL,6,F"We just want some communication but
OL,7,Fwe've heard nothing. I've emailed them
OL,8,Ftwice since they got in touch with us
OL,9,Fand even sent them my mobile number
OL,10,Fbut still have heard nothing.
OL,12,F"All we want is for someone to pick up
OL,13,Fthe phone and call."
OL,15,FMs Wall's experience comes as a huge
OL,16,Fbacklog in the Revenue Service means
OL,17,Fmany tax returns are still being
OL,18,Fprocessed, with some as much as four
OL,19,Fyears old.
