OL,3,CWoman, 84, 'terrified' as tax office
OL,4,Csends her #1,600 bill
OL,6,FFigures from the States of Guernsey
OL,7,Fshow nearly 20% of working people and
OL,8,Fpensioners still waiting for their tax
OL,9,Fassessments from 2020.
OL,11,FThey also highlight that under half of
OL,12,Fall tax returns from 2022 have been
OL,13,Fdealt with.
OL,15,FEach year, all residents over the age
OL,16,Fof 18 are required to fill in a return
OL,17,Fby law.
OL,19,FThe Revenue Service says the COVID
OL,20,Fpandemic and a lack of staff training
OL,21,Fare to blame for the backlog.
