OL,3,CWoman, 84, 'terrified' as tax office
OL,4,Csends her #1,600 bill
OL,6,FScott Bloomfield, Head of Service
OL,7,FDelivery at the Revenue Service,
OL,8,Fexplains: "I appreciate there are some
OL,9,Ffrustrations from the public around
OL,10,Fthe backlog and the team are working
OL,11,Fextremely hard to deal with it.
OL,13,F"I understand some people are sending
OL,14,Frepeat emails and repeat phone calls
OL,15,Fbut we would ask them to give us the
OL,16,Fopportunities to respond to their
OL,17,Ffirst emails so they don't add to the
OL,18,Fbacklog."
